      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-314" title="me-and-jean-011" src="http://www.foodandsugaraddiction.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/me-and-jean-011-300x225.jpg" alt="me-and-jean-011" width="300" height="225" />~</p>
<h1>Hiding Behind My Hair</h1>
<p>Do you do this?</p>
<p>I need to knock on wood before I go any further or the universe will make my hair all fall out for bragging about it! Ha!</p>
<p>Do you have a normal sized bathroom mirror?  Do you avoid the big full length mirror in the hallway?  Or do you just stand there in the perfect position so that you&#8217;ve fooled yourself into thinking you haven&#8217;t gained really all that much weight?</p>
<p>Ok&#8230;back to the hair.</p>
<p>Put the face on, get the hair done!  Gorgeous!    &#8230;..right?</p>
<p>Except for the mess under the face and hair.  But that mirror in the bathroom only shows what you have absolute control over (and really only what I&#8217;m willing to deal with).  That&#8217;s all that really matters right?</p>
<p>Umhm&#8230;I wish it was that easy.</p>
<p>But Ive been hiding behind my hair for much too long.  Will I cut it all off.  NO!  Will I look beyond the bathroom mirror to keep everything in order?  YES!</p>
<p>.</p>
