Similar Posts from Food and Sugar Addiction:&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href='http://www.foodandsugaraddiction.com/food-and-sugar-addiction/notice/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Ever notice&amp;#8230;..'&gt;Ever notice&amp;#8230;..&lt;/a&gt; &lt;small&gt;&amp;#8230;when you are eating properly you have better hair days...&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href='http://www.foodandsugaraddiction.com/food-and-sugar-addiction/recommitment/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: ReCommitment!'&gt;ReCommitment!&lt;/a&gt; &lt;small&gt;[caption id="attachment_17" align="alignleft" width="300" caption="Me "][/caption] I recommitted today! April...&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href='http://www.foodandsugaraddiction.com/food-and-sugar-addiction/awesomest-news/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Looking Your Best &amp;#038; The AWESOMEST News!!!'&gt;Looking Your Best &amp;#038; The AWESOMEST News!!!&lt;/a&gt; &lt;small&gt;There is no reason for you to wait to look...&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/food-and-sugar-addiction/Food_and_Sugar_Addiction-Feeling_Good_While_Loosing.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> </p>
<p>Sometimes we start out on our weight loss journey and we either forget or put off something we have been wanting to do until we&#8217;ve lost &#8220;x&#8221; number of pounds.  <img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-178" title="necklace" src="http://www.foodandsugaraddiction.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/necklace-300x197.jpg" alt="necklace" width="300" height="197" /></p>
<p>Well, that&#8217;s all fine and well.  But why are you waiting?</p>
<p>Did you want to go get a new hairstyle?  Then go!  If you want, make that new hair-do a 5lb reward.  Once you reach that 5lb loss, make your appointment and go!</p>
<p>Have you been wanting that new skin care product you seen at a party, or commercial?  Do you think you don&#8217;t deserve it?  How about pretty jewellery?</p>
<p>Getting my nails done is something I struggled with.  Because in my mind, fat women didn&#8217;t have pretty painted nails.  I know, its a bit warped&#8230;but I never said it was normal in there.  Besides, my hands are the thinnest part of my body.  Have you ever met a 250+ pound woman with a size 5.5 ring finger?  I have the thin pretty hands I associated with thin pretty women.  They just weren&#8217;t attached to the thin body.  No matter, I worked the mess out in my head, and went to have them done. </p>
<p>I loved my pretty red painted finger nails!  They made me feel good. </p>
<p>What are you doing to feel good &amp;  look great while you are loosing weight?</p>
<p>I am making sure I&#8217;m putting my face on everyday.  All of it&#8230;nothing left in the makeup bag!  When I eat properly, exercise and drink my water and green tea, my skin glows.  I just love it!  So I make sure I take care of my skin, and enhance everything I&#8217;ve got!  Even when you are in the morbidly obese category, it&#8217;s still nice when your spouse/partner tells you how pretty or beautiful you look. </p>
<p>Another to-do for me.  Staying out of the clothing stores.  I went earlier this week, and I won&#8217;t be back for a while.  Trying on clothes that just are not properly made for large women is never fun.  From my arm pits up Im still a medium/large&#8230;.the rest is between 2 and 3X.  Going around looking like a linebacker is not my idea of looking and feeling good.</p>
<p>Another feel good to-do.  Being part of a support group that recognizes your accomplishments.  No matter how small those accomplishments are.  Sometimes that &#8220;little&#8221; thing was a really &#8220;big&#8221; thing, and the group &#8220;gets it&#8221;.  </p>
<p>In lieu of clothing I like to buy pretty smelling body wash for the shower.  Its so nice after a hard workout to come out of the shower feeling pretty! </p>
<p>Just be sure you are not trading a <strong>food addiction</strong> for  a shopping addiction.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>How about you?  What do you do?</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
