      <description>Last night&amp;#8217;s supper was steel head trout, Caesar salad and a baked potato.  Now since I had been having issues with cravings and not getting enough food, I thought I&amp;#8217;d try the potato.  In my head I said to myself, &amp;#8220;eat the fish and salad first.  If you still want more, have the potato.&amp;#8221;  Well [...]&lt;p&gt;This post is from: &lt;a href="http://www.foodandsugaraddiction.com"&gt;where you can follow my journey with my Food and Sugar Addiction&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
