      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>There is no reason for you to wait to look good.  I know I&#8217;ve done it in the past.</p>
<p>&#8220;I&#8217;ll wait until I loose 20lbs before I go buy any new cloths&#8221;</p>
<p>&#8220;I&#8217;ll wait until I loose 20lbs before I go get my hair done&#8221;</p>
<p>&#8220;I&#8217;ll wait until I loose 20lbs before I get any new makeup&#8221;</p>
<p>Do you do this?</p>
<p>I am not going to wait this time.  I have a hair appointment on Saturday morning, then when that is finished I&#8217;m heading out to Cold Water Creek for some pretty new tops I seen in their catalogue!  AND I have a 30% off coupon!  Life is good!</p>
<p>Ive also signed signed on with <strong>Mary Kay</strong>!  I know, I know, I&#8217;m the the <strong>Mary Kay</strong> type!!!!!  No kidding!  But I love love love the skin care products.  So I thought I would get set up, and offer a place for folks to go without having to deal with &#8220;<strong>The Mary Kay</strong>&#8221; lady!  So if you don&#8217;t have a Mary Kay Lady go here to get one! <a href="http://www.marykay.com/wintergirl">www.marykay.com/wintergirl</a></p>
<p>Besides when I put my face on for special events, I like it to last the night.  There is nothing worse than going to all the trouble to look good, only to have it all soaked in or brushed off after about 2 hours.  Mary Kay has some amazing products that help combat that problem!</p>
<h2>Ok on to the AWESOMEST news!!!!</h2>
<p>My Personal Trainer (Michelle Mullen who is the owner of  <a href="http://www.healthandfitsolutions.com">www.healthandfitsolutions.com</a> ) is going to be working with me right here on the blog!!  That means she gets to <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">yell at</span> support me&#8230;here!</p>
<p>We will be including weekly weigh ins, measurements, video, podcasts, and visits to some skinny chick&#8217;s fridges!!  Its going to be awesome!</p>
<p>Here is the thing&#8230;..I&#8217;m scared!  Of what?  Of succeeding.  I need to get out of my own way, and get to where I want to be and to <strong>stay</strong> there!</p>
<p>I&#8217;ve been fighting <strong>obesity</strong> and <strong>addiction </strong>for too long.  It got old 25 yrs ago!!  So Michelle said she is happy to be the &#8220;cement&#8221; in my commitment!</p>
<p>Keep watching, we plan to do some fun/cool things for you all to peek in on.</p>
<p>Remember if you want to comment, head over to the &#8220;About&#8221; page and leave a comment there.  Im hoping to have the comments on this page fixed this week.</p>
