<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;">The crazy cravings showed up last night. Do you ever get these?<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>The kind of cravings that send you into a bit of a frenzy.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>Not that anyone would see or notice it.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>But the crap going on your head is going berserk?<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">   </span>Keeping yourself a from eating everything in the house becomes a<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>monumental task!</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;">Well, that’s what was happening to me last night.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;">I had been wanting something sweet all day and all night.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>I had been putting myself off all day.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>I didn’t want to go out by myself last night, because I knew that was my perfect time to eat.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>While I was alone.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;">My first thoughts yesterday were, my husband is at work.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>I’ll just walk over to the market and pick up a few things.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>I can have everything eaten and all the garbage tossed out and he’d never know.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>I thought, yes that’s a good idea I’ll do that.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>But the dieting Robin kept putting it off.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>I’d look at the clock and think, “ok, I’ve got 2 hours yet, I can still go to the market.” I managed to put all that off until he came home at 4:30.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>Then he wanted to go for coffee.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>I really didn’t want to leave the house.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>You know sometimes, just leaving that space you have made “safe” from any external triggers and going anywhere else would break thru that barrier you’ve built for yourself.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;">Off we went, had our coffee, and a little ride around the marina.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>Ok, that wasn’t so bad.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>We got home, I made supper and everything was ok.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>My inner fatchick wasn’t messing with my head. </span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;">She started up again about an hour after I had eaten.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>No I wasn’t hungry, I just wanted something sweet. I wanted it KNOW!<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">   </span>I had finished all the yogurt covered raisins, had the fruit salad, had a muffin…but all this just wasn’t satisfying the sweet attack I seemed to be in the throws of.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;">I just kept putting it off.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>I had enough stuff yesterday I shouldn’t have.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>I had more than enough to eat.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;">But you know when you want something, you try to replace it with something else.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>In my case I kept trying to replace it with other foods.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>Guess I shouldn’t have done that.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;">My last effort came in the form of orville redebacker popcorn.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>Thinking in my warped brain, it’s a grain that will turn to sugar in my system and that should make everything happy.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>Nope that wasn’t it either.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;">I finished the popcorn, and I lasted until 10 o’clock when hubby went to bed.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>I got up off the couch, and proceeded to make 2 sandwiches.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>One cheese, and one chicken.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>More of that sneak eating.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>I should have just gone to bed with him.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>But by 10 I was ready to stuff my inner fatchick.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>I was so tired of fighting her.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>Well, it didn’t work.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>Because I’m still looking for sugar this morning.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 4.8pt 4.8pt 0pt;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;">I know I can build a wall around her to keep her quiet.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>That wall is eating properly all the time.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span>Keeping the sugar cravings to little twinges of desire rather than all out wars against my true desires.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">  </span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 4.8pt 0pt;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 4.8pt 0pt;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;">My true desires being, wanting to be fit, happy and healthy.  I spent today cooking and getting things ready for tomorrow morning.  I have lunches and snacks prepared for the week.  Breakfast is always the same thing, so I don&#8217;t have any issues there.  I will just have to deal with suppers.  I did however, clean a head of romaine lettuce and it is ready to be made into ceasar salad in a pinch.  I have no excuses.  I will not let the <strong>food addiction</strong> or the <strong>sugar addiction</strong> take over and stop me from being the best I know I can be. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></p>
