      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Pick your diet.<br />
Go over your list you wrote out the other day, add other reasons if you have come up with them.</p>
<p>Did you pick your diet?<br />
Mine is Atkins for 2-3 weeks, then I switch over to weight watchers with low carb choices.<br />
Finally switching to a combo of both, counting calories and watching fat grams.</p>
<p>I know it sounds convoluted, but after all these years of dieting, I know what works for me. This works for me!</p>
<p>Just pick your one diet, then have a back up incase you want to switch over after a couple weeks.</p>
<p>The point of this is to not feel like you have failed at this. Just pick up the next one, and soldier on!</p>
<p>Today is actually day 3 for me&#8230;.I&#8217;ll post that later on tonight.</p>
<p>So what did you do today to feel absolutely wonderful?<br />
I went for a color consultation with my Mary Kay lady! Ive never been a mary kay kinda person, never wanted to be bothered with all that stuff. But I love their skin care products! Especially having pcos I have to be careful what I use. My facial skin tends to thicken when I use exfoliators. This stuff doesnt do that. It also helps with my dark chin too&#8230;.evens out my skin tone. I love it&#8230;.so much I will probably have a link to the products here in the blog within the next couple days.</p>
<p>Ok&#8230;so what did you do?(I have pretty purple eye shadow on to show off my sparkly brown eyes) LOL</p>
<p>Have an awesome day everyone!</p>
