      <description>This is the dress I had purchased a few years ago. Deep green velvet! I wanted to wear it at christmas that year. (I dont remember what year?!?!) But it will get worn this year!
Alright on to today&amp;#8217;s task!
Getting my list of reasons for loosing weight posted.
