      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-25" title="green velvet dress" src="http://www.foodandsugaraddiction.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/dress-225x300.jpg" alt="green velvet dress" width="225" height="300" />This is the dress I had purchased a few years ago. Deep green velvet! I wanted to wear it at christmas that year. (I dont remember what year?!?!) But it will get worn this year!</p>
<p>Alright on to today&#8217;s task!</p>
<p>Getting my list of reasons for loosing weight posted.</p>
<p>Day One<br />
Week One</p>
<p><strong>Creating a Foundation for Success</strong></p>
<p>Today’s task was to write down the reasons I want to loose weight.<br />
Here they are…</p>
<p>1. I will feel better.<br />
2. I will look better.<br />
3. I will be healthier.<br />
4. I will be more physically active and able to keep up with my daughter<br />
5. My nice clothing will fit.<br />
6. I will be able to wear what I like rather than what fits that day.<br />
7. I will have more energy<br />
8. I tend to be more organized<br />
9. I will be more in control of<br />
• My eating<br />
• My feelings<br />
• Of the amount of weight lost<br />
• Of the inner dialogue that can be so tormenting!<br />
10. Keep any health issues related to obesity at bay.<br />
11. Because when I am in control I have many more “happy days”.<br />
12. I will enjoy exercising<br />
13. I will look forward to bike rides and hikes</p>
<p>If you are looking for <a href="http://astore.amazon.com/buffagraph0b-20/detail/0848731913">The Beck Diet Solution Weight Loss Workbook</a>  just click on the title and it will take you right to it.</p>
<p>Tomorrow&#8217;s task &#8220;commit to a diet&#8221;</p>
<p>OK, all that is out of the way.</p>
<p>Im off to meet with my Personal Trainer after almost a year!!  *eek*  I&#8217;ll let you know how it all went! </p>
<p>If anyone reading here has had any experience at the <strong>Best Fitness Center</strong>, please let me know.  I&#8217;d love some feedback before I go check it out.</p>
